Class CrimeSummaryDetailed

  • java.lang.Object
    • benak.tomas.crimemonitor.library.CrimeSummaryWithUtvarBase
      • benak.tomas.crimemonitor.library.CrimeSummaryWithUtvarAndIntervalBase

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UtvarAndIntervalBasedCrimeSummary, UtvarBasedCrimeSummary, java.io.Serializable

    public class CrimeSummaryDetailed
extends CrimesSummaryBasic
implements java.io.Serializable
    A class used to provide the crime statistics for a particular kind of crime.

    A kind of crime is identified by a TSK identifier.

    The statistics provided are:

    • the calculated number of cases when a crime of the given kind occurred
    • the
    • crime count monthly histogram (see CrimeMonthHistogramObservation for a more detailed definition of a crime count monthly histogram)
    Author:
    Tom
